# Bajablue Tours — Environment Variables
# NEVER commit .env with real values. Only .env.example goes in git.

# ============================================================================
# WeTravel — booking system
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Real values come from the Bajablue team once WeTravel trips are published. Until
# these are set, BookingDrawer falls back to a "Booking opens soon — message
# us on WhatsApp" CTA rather than sending guests to a broken URL.
#
# Source: Bajablue team → WeTravel dashboard → each trip's public URL
# Onboarding wizard step 2 captures these values from the client team.
# Contract tie: Baja Blue Phase 2 — booking/payment integration.
# ============================================================================

# Public trip URLs (browser-readable, NEXT_PUBLIC_ prefix required)
# NEXT_PUBLIC_WETRAVEL_OCEAN_SAFARI_URL=https://www.wetravel.com/trips/ocean-safari-bajablue-tours-XXXXX
# NEXT_PUBLIC_WETRAVEL_BLUE_EXPEDITION_URL=https://www.wetravel.com/trips/blue-expedition-bajablue-tours-XXXXX
# NEXT_PUBLIC_WETRAVEL_MASTER_SEAFARI_URL=https://www.wetravel.com/trips/master-seafari-bajablue-tours-XXXXX

# Server-side secrets (never NEXT_PUBLIC_ — never exposed to the browser)
# Used by the future /api/webhooks/wetravel handler to verify booking events.
# WETRAVEL_API_KEY=
# WETRAVEL_WEBHOOK_SECRET=

# ============================================================================
# Analytics
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Provided after the client grants Google Workspace + Meta Business Manager access.
# Vercel Analytics + Speed Insights are wired in via @vercel/analytics already
# and need no env vars (auto-discovers project from deployment).
# ============================================================================

# NEXT_PUBLIC_GA_ID=G-XXXXXXXXXX
# NEXT_PUBLIC_META_PIXEL_ID=XXXXXXXXXX
# NEXT_PUBLIC_UMAMI_WEBSITE_ID=
# NEXT_PUBLIC_UMAMI_SCRIPT_URL=https://cloud.umami.is/script.js

# ============================================================================
# Telegram — admin ticket alerts + onboarding step notifications
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Bot token comes from @BotFather (onboarding wizard step 10).
# Chat ID is the private admin Telegram chat ID.
# ============================================================================

# TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN=
# TELEGRAM_CHAT_ID=

# ============================================================================
# Onboarding wizard
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Token in the wizard URL — controls who can submit onboarding answers.
# Already set in Vercel production env. Rotate by changing here + Vercel.
# ============================================================================

# ONBOARDING_TOKEN=

# ============================================================================
# Firebase Admin — Firestore writes for onboarding + admin features
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Server-only (no NEXT_PUBLIC_ prefix). All three required for admin SDK.
# ============================================================================

# FIREBASE_ADMIN_PROJECT_ID=
# FIREBASE_ADMIN_CLIENT_EMAIL=
# FIREBASE_ADMIN_PRIVATE_KEY=

# ============================================================================
# Search Console / verification
# ============================================================================

# NEXT_PUBLIC_GOOGLE_SITE_VERIFICATION=

# ============================================================================
# Video hosting / CDN
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Set this after 4K video files are uploaded to a CDN/static video origin.
# The app keeps the same /videos/... paths and prepends this host at runtime.
#
# Current launch fallback:
# NEXT_PUBLIC_VIDEO_CDN_BASE_URL=https://pub-7e0ec8f0f0714e17bc76dafc4a1f78de.r2.dev
#
# Final branded domain once bajablue.mx is managed in Cloudflare DNS:
# NEXT_PUBLIC_VIDEO_CDN_BASE_URL=https://media.bajablue.mx
#
# For Cloudflare Stream/Mux HLS player IDs, use the hosting manifest in
# docs/video-hosting-and-ai-upscale.md before swapping the component strategy.
# ============================================================================

# NEXT_PUBLIC_VIDEO_CDN_BASE_URL=

# ============================================================================
# Legacy / inactive — keep here for reference only
# ============================================================================

# CLOUDFLARE_STREAM_TOKEN=
# CLOUDFLARE_ACCOUNT_ID=
# SQUARESPACE_ACCESS_TOKEN=
